{"id": "1187553907589795850", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "没有。我玩图鲁带的珊，加固用好的话可以抗很多伤害。朵儿改版后，即使快速击杀对面C位，拉起来后40血还是很难再杀掉，甚至会刷新对方输出的技能，尤其是毒妈这种的。并不是说骑士不好，而是骑士的表现没有以前那么稳定了。除了点名以外，骑士能做的事情很少。", "timestamp": "2023-12-22T00:35:15.254000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["454232816893427713"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1187234874239746148", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1187554338516779128", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "神王图鲁是一定要带拉蒙娜的。朵儿也是必带的，这种情况下带不带骑士是需要考虑的。赌那一张点名是不稳定的选择。", "timestamp": "2023-12-22T00:36:57.995000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1187555584829038774", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "现在传说局有三赌：神王、毒、点名。其中点名来的早不足以击杀百血图鲁。来的晚可能骑士已经死了。这三张卡上手的速度决定了对局的走向。", "timestamp": "2023-12-22T00:41:55.139000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
