{"id": "1187665407113445436", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "203498180946558976", "author_name": "eceniht", "author_bot": false, "content": "沒錯 單雙C問題就是\n圖魯隊整隊只需要算圖魯傷害 其他卡都是增減益嘲諷 打牌快又簡單\n其他哪怕是多塞個拉蒙娜都能算到超時\n\n毒媽可能像你說的跟圖魯五五開 但我近10場一場都沒遇到 全都圖魯或AI ㄆ", "timestamp": "2023-12-22T07:58:18.812000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["632653171642335272"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1187618765056249866", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1187665991300284468", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "203498180946558976", "author_name": "eceniht", "author_bot": false, "content": "朵爾改單復活 之前復活還能直接戳死 現在圖魯一復活40HP 直接打不死又給你活好久 真的改動全改在BUF圖魯上面 又是抽限定的勝利", "timestamp": "2023-12-22T08:00:38.093000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1187666978308112446", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "203498180946558976", "author_name": "eceniht", "author_bot": false, "content": "打PVP第一周就覺得該改的是牌位數量 爬那麼多牌位爬到死才會覺得要打很久\n不是改對戰時間 改到水母大刀凱哥潘迪亞原本一堆隊伍能玩現在就剩圖魯毒媽", "timestamp": "2023-12-22T08:04:33.414000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
